4-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-4-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west@2000x1270-4-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）</a>宣布，本月初有一系列反犹太社交媒体帖子之后，他“不是纳粹”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-unaired-footage-fox-news-anti-semitic-comments-3326989">凭借他的“白人生命问题”的特技，坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）终于达到了没有回报的地步？</a></strong></li></ul><p>在星期三晚上（2月19日），这位有争议的说唱歌手带到了X（以前是Twitter），分享了“进一步反思”，他“意识到我不是纳粹”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">经过进一步的反思，我意识到我不是纳粹</p><p>-  Ye（@kanyewest） <a href="https://twitter.com/kanyewest/status/1892307950670057946?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2025年2月19日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>该帖子发表<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">在本月初在社交媒体平台上在社交媒体平台上推出了一系列引起争议的帖子</a>之后，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-releases-new-song-beauty-and-the-beast-before-stripping-yeezy-site-to-only-sell-swastika-t-shirt-3836729">在其网站上卖出了一件Swastika T恤</a>。</p><p>他的发帖狂欢 - 本月早些时候是在格莱美奖开始的 - 看到他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">向犹太人社区撤销了他过去的反犹太人言论</a>，然后继续宣布自己为“纳粹”，并写道：“我爱希特勒”，以及赞美亿万富翁和X所有者埃隆<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-sparks-backlash-with-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3830625">·</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/elon-musk">马斯克（Elon Musk</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/elon-musk-sparks-backlash-with-nazi-like-gesture-at-trump-inauguration-3830625">就职典礼</a>。</p><p>进一步的帖子使他嘲笑其他边缘化社区，声称“奴隶制是一种选择”等。然后，他擦拭了Yeezy的网站，并开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-releases-new-song-beauty-and-the-beast-before-stripping-yeezy-site-to-only-sell-swastika-t-shirt-3836729">在胸部出售一件白色T恤，上面有一个大障碍标志</a>，在他的网站上被列为“ HH-01”，可能是对“ Heil Hitler” Chant的引用。</p><p>该网站<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-shut-down-kanye-wests-yeezy-website-for-selling-swastika-t-shirt-matthew-koma-responds-with-fuck-ye-merch-3837155">后来被Shopify取消</a>，尽管在线零售商后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shopify-says-kanye-wests-site-was-removed-over-fraud-potential-not-swastika-t-shirt-3837621">表示，由于欺诈的可能性，艺术家的网站被取消了 - 不是因为它出售了Swastika T恤</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3838836" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3838836" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3838836" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kanye-west-2019@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3838836" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West），2019年。信贷：吉尔伯特·卡拉斯基洛（Gilbert Carrasquillo）/GC图像</figcaption></figure><p>狂欢看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-x-account-has-been-deactivated-after-bizarre-weekend-rant-3836418">他的X帐户被删除并停用了</a>，后来证实说唱歌手已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-dropped-by-talent-agency-following-anti-semitic-posts-3837245">被他的人才机构放弃，</a>他的前任参谋长辞去了Yeezy Company。</p><p>坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）的X帐户后来恢复了，此后，说唱歌手说他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-had-swastika-t-shirt-idea-for-over-eight-years-3838835">有“超过八年”的T恤的想法</a>。最近，他还认为，他的最后一次“横冲直撞”是“ 90％的犹太人证明”，然后才暗示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanyes-twitter-and-instagram-accounts-locked-after-antisemitic-posts-3325446">了几年前他臭名昭著的反犹太人长篇小说</a>，其中包括许多其他古怪的说法，看到他告诉他犹太社区他们需要他们需要为大屠杀<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-tells-jewish-people-to-forgive-hitler-compares-porn-to-the-holocaust-3361860">“原谅希特勒”</a> - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-apologises-jewish-community-antisemitic-comments-3563267">他为2023年的评论道歉</a>。</p><p> His rants earlier this month also saw him <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-is-never-apologising-for-my-jewish-comments-and-claims-to-have-dominion-over-bianca-censori-fuck-all-that-woke-shit-3835994">declare “dominion” over his wife Bianca Censori</a> after they attended the Grammys red carpet event, where <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grammys-2025-kanye-west-shows-up-with-wife-bianca-censori-who-reveals-shocking-see-through-dress-3833867">she wore a see-through dress that revealed her naked figure</a> . He also posted a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-voices-support-for-diddy-and-chris-brown-free-puff-3835815">series of tweets in support of Diddy and Chris Brown and urged for the former to be released from prison amid sexual abuse allegations</a> .</p><p> In the time since the rant on social media, Kanye West&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kanye-west-ty-dolla-sign-vultures-1-review-lyrics-tracklist-3585917">&#39;Vultures&#39;</a> collaborator <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ty-dolla-ign-condemns-hate-speech-following-kanye-wests-anti-semitic-posts-and-swastika-t-shirt-controversy-3837549">Ty Dolla $ign has condemned his hate speech</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charlie-puth-begs-kanye-west-to-stop-promoting-incredibly-dangerous-messages-and-swastika-tee-3837062">Charlie Puth begged West to stop promoting “incredibly dangerous” messages,</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/friends"><em>Friends</em></a> star <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/david-schwimmer-calls-for-action-against-kanye-west-after-nazi-comments-silence-is-complicity-3836363">David Schwimmer called for action to be taken against the rapper</a> for his hate-filled “Nazi” posts, arguing that “silence is complicity”.</p><p> Elsewhere, Ye has been <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-sued-for-discrimination-and-accused-of-texting-hail-hitler-to-jewish-yeezy-employee-3837691">sued for discrimination by a former Yeezy employee, and accused of texting “Hail Hitler” to a Jewish staff member</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-has-come-to-the-realisation-that-hes-not-a-nazi-after-reflection-3839623">Kanye West has “come to the realisation” that he&#39;s “not a Nazi” after “reflection”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 Sheffield's Leadmill loses eviction court battle with landlord – but vow to fight on https://www.nme.com/news/music/sheffields-leadmill-loses-eviction-court-battle-with-landlord-but-vow-to-fight-on-3839619?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sheffields-leadmill-loses-eviction-court-battle-with-landlord-but-vow-to-fight-onSurej Singh Thu, 20 Feb 2025 02:14:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3839619 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="The Leadmill in Sheffield where Def Leppard performed their &quot;One Night Only&quot; gig. Picture date: Friday May 19, 2023." decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Building owners issued an eviction notice in 2022, leaving the iconic venue&#39;s future up in the air</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sheffields-leadmill-loses-eviction-court-battle-with-landlord-but-vow-to-fight-on-3839619">Sheffield&#39;s Leadmill loses eviction court battle with landlord – but vow to fight on</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="The Leadmill in Sheffield where Def Leppard performed their &quot;One Night Only&quot; gig. Picture date: Friday May 19, 2023." decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Leadmill@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Sheffield&#39;s Leadmill has lost its eviction court battle with its landlord, leaving its future uncertain – the iconic has venue has issued a statement promising that it will continue to fight on.</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/sheffield-leadmill-arctic-monkeys-closes-we-all-lose-something-3196736"><b>If Sheffield&#39;s Leadmill – the venue that helped break Arctic Monkeys – goes, we all lose something</b></a></li></ul><p> Electric Group, the owners of the 900-capacity venue&#39;s building, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">served an eviction notice on their tenants The Leadmill Ltd in March 2022</a> , which sparked an <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">outcry across the music industry and from gig-goers</a> . The Leadmill Ltd own the trademark for the venue&#39;s name – meaning a new venue in a different building could retain the name and branding of the original.</p><p> Since first opening its doors in 1980, the venue has hosted early shows from <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">Arctic Monkeys</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kings-of-leon">Kings Of Leon</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a> , and remains a popular live music and clubbing spot.</p><p> Last night (February 19), The Leadmill issued a statement on social media regarding the court&#39;s ruling against the venue in favour of its landlords. The Leadmill wrote: “While this is a challenging and upsetting moment for our venue, we want to reassure our supporters, artists, and the wider community that there is no immediate timeline for what happens next.” </p><figure id="attachment_3286984" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3286984" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3286984" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Richard-Hawley-Jarvis-Cocker-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3286984" class="wp-caption-text"> Richard Hawley and Jarvis Cocker onstage at the Leadmill in Sheffield on August 9, 2022. Credit: Tom Sunderland</figcaption></figure><p> Leadmill说，目前没有明确的道路前进，它正在“积极咨询”其法律顾问，并“将继续致力于耗尽一切可能的法律途径，以确保我们的未来，保留我们的员工并保护我们的场地。”</p><p> The court battle isn&#39;t just about saving the venue, The Leadmill says: “It&#39;s personal. The Leadmill isn&#39;t just bricks and mortar; it&#39;s a home.我们的许多团队在这里长大，在这里工作了15年以上，并致力于创造令人难以置信的活动和经验。 We are real people, with a deep love for what we do, and we never imaged we&#39;d be facing something like this. But we are in it together, doing everything we can to fight for the place that means so much to us and to so many others.”</p><p> Leadmill指出自驱逐新闻首次爆发以来，该场地的文化影响及其获得的支持，重申了它的“不仅仅是一个场地”：“这是一个具有45年培养艺术家历史的文化机构，支持艺术家的历史基层音乐，并为谢菲尔德及其他地区提供了重要的创造力。”</p><p>该场地还向顾客和任何有门票的人确认，除非另有说明，否则所有计划编程将按计划进行的节目和活动。</p><p>在结束的讲话中，Leadmill敦促其支持者“继续与我们站在一起”，因为他们“在这场战斗的下一个阶段中导航”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGREpiRzatI/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60